body: TF_BUILTIN(ArrayPrototypePop, CodeStubAssembler) in builtins/builtins-array-gen.cc — fast-path implementation with checks for BranchIfFastJSArray, EnsureArrayLengthWritable, copy-on-write elements check, backing-store shrink check, element load/store and TailCallJSBuiltin(Builtin::kArrayPop, ...) fallback to runtime. Code lines: builtins/builtins-array-gen.cc (TF_BUILTIN ArrayPrototypePop)
